Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:10990,12075}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:12534,13910}Let's walk home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:14285,14786}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:17.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:16037,17121}We heard the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:19.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:17247,19332}You've been asked by the Mayor…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:19415,22335}to help arrest that\Nphantom thief, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:24.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:23795,24796}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:24921,26047}Yup, it sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:26130,27632}Wow! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:27840,30009}They say you did great\Non the last case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:30927,34430}How you protected the\Njewels from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:37.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:34722,37350}It was all over the papers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:39.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:37684,39102}I read that article, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:41.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:39602,41938}It said, "He protected the Blue\NMeteorite from St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:44.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:41980,44315}and helped in the arrest of Umido."\NThat's how it went?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:45.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:44399,45483}Yup, that's how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:49.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:46317,49571}But you let St. Tail get away,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:53.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:50613,53074}That's why I've been\Nasked to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:57.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:53616,57453}I'm the only one who's\Nseen her up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:59205,61124}See! This is my official permit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:02.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:61708,62709}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63626,66129}It's the badge I gotfrom the Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:10.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:67130,70800}All I have to do is show this\Nand I can get in to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71301,72927}Hey, that's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:16.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:73136,76264}Does your dad know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:77599,79684}He got himself all worked up over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:21.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:79767,81894}He wants me to get the job done,\Ndo or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:83855,86941}Isn't that St. Tail's first failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:27.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,87650}Failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:30.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88234,90612}And her nemesis is Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91029,93531}I've got to hand it to you,\Nyou're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93615,94782}It's true, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94866,96409}Ain't it fabulous?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96534,98661}Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:39.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98953,99996}You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:40.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100079,100622}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101372,103082}I haven't failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:45.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104375,105960}Whose voice was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106336,107295}Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109589,112800}Oh, Meimi,\Ndon't let it bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112925,115219}I've never failed once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115637,116596}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116679,119390}Why don't you drop by the\Nchurch for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119515,121851}I haven't failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126648,128608}He's really asking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128900,131569}As if a guy like that\Ncould catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131819,134489}My, you're fired up,\Naren't you Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134614,135740}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:16.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135823,136449}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136532,138451}Your mission this time is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143289,144499}This tiara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145500,147502}It's called Electra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:28.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147669,148586}Electra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152131,154926}Named for the star\Nin the Subaru constellation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155259,157053}Also known as "the missing one".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:42.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158137,162600}It was stolen from someone by Egami,\Nwho lives on 7th avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163601,167980}Let's return it to\Nits rightful owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168523,169524}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169816,170441}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170858,172360}This wouldn't be a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172610,174404}You heard, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174487,177448}Asuka Jr. received a badge from the\NMayor, granting investigation power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177490,179992}He's all wound up\Nand ready to leap into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:05.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181494,185540}Meimi, you're not afraid of\NAsuka Jr., are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185707,186416}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187875,190128}If that's so, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190503,192964}Let's forget about this caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193047,194048}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194549,195717}You're kidding, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196217,197635}Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197885,200096}You just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:26.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202098,206310}I'm not afraid of a bumbling\Ndetective like him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209105,210440}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214318,217029}St. Tail… Isn't she wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217697,220742}She's exactly like me\Nwhen I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220867,221534}Aww shoot…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222744,223703}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227206,228750}What's the matter, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229417,231461}The balloons…\Nwhere have I put them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232336,233171}Balloons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233504,235047}The ones I use for my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237008,240136}Aren't they supposed to\Nbe in your trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240470,243306}Yes, but they're not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247685,249604}Only the balloons have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250396,252648}Papa, are you sure they're missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254317,255985}Remember what happened\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256652,258696}You put two socks on one foot and…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259030,261365}went around saying\N"Where's my other sock?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261741,263409}Oh, don't bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266037,267455}Anyway, it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:40.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279884,280927}Hey! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281093,282470}Asuka! Up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282512,283137}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286724,287850}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:52.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288184,292230}"I'll be picking up the Electra\Ntonight – St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293606,295942}It's a note from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296192,298903}Hey, it's a challenge! What class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300488,301405}You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301531,302490}This is fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303074,304200}She's the phantom, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304492,306035}She's got real guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310456,313000}I'll be ready for you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316754,320758}Meimi? Just what is this\Nall about exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:27.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323010,327849}Hey have you heard? St. Tail\Nsent Asuka Jr. a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327890,329225}Don't you think that's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329308,330351}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331769,335731}Why do you think she told Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336148,338109}It does seem too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338359,339151}Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342864,345616}Maybe St. Tail and Asuka Jr. are…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345700,346701}No doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347201,349287}The two of them are in this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354041,355376}So…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357461,360214}St. Tail has sent a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360840,364260}I won 't let anyone get\Nmy tiara, Electra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:10.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366387,370182}Sir, there is a rumor going around…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:11.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370766,371726}Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:17.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373603,377273}What! St. Tail and Asuka Jr.\Nare working together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:18.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377857,378816}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383029,385740}You're Mr. Egami, the tiara's owner,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386198,387366}And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:32.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388534,392121}The Mayor asked me to assist in\Nthe St. Tail investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392246,393205}My name is Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395750,398920}Oh, so you're Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399545,401130}I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404967,406177}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411933,414560}I leave all security in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414936,416103}Yes, sir! I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416604,418564}Please catch St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419482,421984}No matter what the rumors may say…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422276,424278}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425863,428032}Rumors? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:09.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428616,429700}You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:13.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430117,433663}There's great doubt\Nabout you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:19.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434997,439961}It's suspected that you\Nare St. Tail's accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440378,441879}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442964,445466}She sent you a note, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445967,447343}Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447426,448177}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:32.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448386,452348}I'm sure it's all just rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:38.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453849,458896}For the sake of clearing your name,\Nplease protect my Electra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459397,460815}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461440,463192}Who'd want to work with\Nthat girl, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,464735}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466570,469073}Everything is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469615,471993}The tiara is in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472994,474954}Everything has gone well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475997,478749}The fool trusted me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480459,483587}I'd never be tricked\Nby a brat like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485506,488342}I'll set them both up and turn him in\Nto the police along with St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490094,492179}By the way, Mr. Egami,\Nwhere is Electra right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:16.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493639,496767}The truth is, hearing about the\Nchallenge made me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496851,500813}I couldn't leave it in the mansion,\Nso I've hidden it in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501731,504525}You're really a worrier, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504734,506527}So, where did you hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508571,509530}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517163,519415}At the top of that clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522293,525254}Why hide it in such a difficult place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525629,527048}Where exactly in the\Nclock tower is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527548,529175}On the face of the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529467,531010}Behind the hour hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540394,541145}What!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541312,543814}On the face of the clock,\Nbehind the hour hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545191,547485}That's a tough place to get it from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:12.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548277,552114}Actually, I know for sure he's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552531,554533}The tiara is really behind\Nthe minute hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554909,557912}How did you get information like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558621,562541}Egami is trying to frame Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562917,564668}What? A trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:50.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586774,590861}There's a rumor that Asuka Jr.\Nis St. Tail's accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:55.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591237,595741}Egami would never tell him the true\Nhiding place of the tiara, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:04.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598369,604667}He lied so Asuka Jr. will be\Narrested along with St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605042,606502}That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606752,610047}It's all because of that note you sent\Nto challenge him, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610923,612049}You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:17.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613300,617012}I guess so… He's getting set up,\Nbecause of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:26.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619056,626856}If you steal the tiara from the minute\Nhand, Asuka Jr.'s name is cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627606,628566}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629733,632820}My lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:38.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637950,638784}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641412,642329}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644748,646292}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660848,663851}May the blessing of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666187,667688}But I'll tell you this…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668314,671192}I'm not doing this to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:12.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671692,672776}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673527,675070}Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:33.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692963,693964}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695299,697843}Do you intend to sit there and\Nstake out the place all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698594,700137}Not all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700846,703641}St. Tail will be coming at exactly 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705017,706060}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:50.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706977,710522}The only time St. Tail can reach\Nthe hour hand is 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711690,714735}To steal Electra at any other time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715903,717112}is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717780,718656}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718948,721575}I'm counting on you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724078,725579}I'm waiting for you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:13.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728457,733254}What a fool! You don't know that\NElectra is behind the minute hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:17.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734046,737341}At 6:00, everyone will see\Nthat you and St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737424,738926}are both idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762700,764660}Looks like there isn't any security.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767162,769373}I have to climb the clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783846,784972}That's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:17.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793397,797151}Almost 6:00. Time for St. Tail\Nto make her appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798777,800487}Sir! We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800571,803073}What's wrong?\NWhy are you so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:28.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803824,808037}Sir! Someone is climbing the ladder\Non the side of the clock tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808287,809038}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809413,812041}That ladder leads to the top stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812624,813250}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836398,839151}Okay! St. Tail, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839568,840486}Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841820,842363}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:07.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842780,847034}What a beautiful moon.\NI'm so happy you waited for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847618,849036}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849745,851246}Why are you up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851413,853040}I know where it's really hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:16.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853123,856585}Electra is behind the minute hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858295,860089}Behind the minute hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:32.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869348,872893}Well, that's it. I've got Electra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877439,879525}My Electra is being stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879650,881860}Wait! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882069,883195}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885030,886198}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886281,889159}Mr. Egami, you said the Electra was\Nbehind the hour hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889201,890202}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890953,893414}St. Tail, I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898877,900504}You can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900796,902756}Don't move, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906802,909263}It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923777,926655}That's the balloon she used\Nto send me the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927531,929199}Bye, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930033,931160}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932411,933454}You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950679,951430}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:59.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956560,959313}This time,\NI'll bust that big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960564,962858}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963233,964276}Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980709,982794}This will get my Electra back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987716,989676}Brat! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004483,1006443}Cut it out!! …Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010906,1012199}Stop… please…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019331,1022834}I wasn't trying to protect you!\NDon't misunderstand what I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027422,1028298}Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028423,1030217}Keep sending me those challenges!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030467,1031927}Give me a fair chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032344,1034346}I'll get you sooner or later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034555,1036557}Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:25.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042312,1045691}I don't know why,\Nbut it's fun to have him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:29.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046024,1049695}And I'll do anything\Nto keep on feeling this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057619,1058579}Good Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058870,1059788}Good Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069464,1072092}The real owner was very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:54.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072342,1074636}She says, "Thank you for\Nreturning Electra".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075762,1077973}Hang on a sec.\NI'll catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078140,1078807}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082102,1084980}That old man…\Nhe even had me fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085856,1087190}Hey, great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087733,1089693}You're a hero in the papers, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089860,1091528}You caught another crook, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091612,1094823}Yeah… but St. Tail still got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095073,1097868}Well, you can give us the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100037,1101246}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102247,1103498}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105042,1106668}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106793,1109254}Glad to hear your name's been cleared.\NThat's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109630,1111048}Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:37.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112841,1117095}And you let St. Tail get away again.\NI hear you're on bad terms with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117804,1120140}What do you mean, "again"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120307,1123101}Anyway, it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124519,1127731}Ah, she's a hopeless case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129691,1131652}But that cut…! Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138867,1140994}Well, hang in there till next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:07.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143497,1147626}I know that St. Tail is a girl\Nabout the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149211,1150379}It couldn't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151713,1153048}Nah, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:32.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168021,1172818}St. Tail Mini-Theatre!\N"The Great Hot Potato Chase!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:45.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181076,1185414}Autumn leaves.\NIt'll be fall in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:47.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186957,1187958}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188208,1190669}I'm at the best part of the story,\Nso don't talk to me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190877,1193338}Autumn, is a season for reading…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193547,1196633}But how about reading something\Nother than comic books sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197884,1200512}Ah… "Autumn of Romance."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200804,1203390}I'd like to be chased by…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:07.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203473,1207102}a handsome, passionate lover,\Nlike the girl in this comic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:15.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207477,1215235}But Meimi, you do have a passionate\Nperson chasing after you, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:22.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217779,1222242}Hot potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227289,1229624}Meimi! How un-ladylike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:33.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229708,1233462}My, Seira.\NWasn't that your stomach just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:42.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233587,1242137}That's right ladies! Come and get them!\NThey're hot and sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243263,1246683}Autumn's the season to\Ncrave sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247350,1250687}Stone-baked sweet potatoes!\NHot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250771,1253148}Well then Meimi, please go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:59.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253482,1259321}Hey, just a minute!\NWhy should I have to go buy it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:05.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259654,1265035}I'm a servant of God. Sister told me\Nit's forbidden for me to buy and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265285,1268622}Oh really? Then that means I don't\Nhave to get one for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:16.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269498,1276838}Buying is forbidden, but it's fine\Nto have a kind friend share a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278882,1280842}I always have to play these roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281218,1283220}Someday, Seira's gonna get punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:27.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283678,1287557}Natural and delicious!\NStone-baked hot potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287641,1289684}Nobody's looking… here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289810,1291311}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291394,1293355}Hey! Haneoka, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294815,1296024}That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297609,1299319}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299778,1301738}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302405,1304825}Wha… what?\NIt's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305450,1307702}What about you!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307953,1309162}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309454,1312374}I'm in the middle of an investigation\Nto catch St. Tail's tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:53.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312582,1313500}Don't even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:56.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313625,1316336}St. Tail isn't a slowpoke\Nthat you'd be able to catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:57.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316837,1317921}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:01.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318004,1321883}The Mayor himself commissioned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322467,1324261}So don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324886,1326304}Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:07.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326388,1327806}This isn't a Samurai movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327889,1330475}Who'd be impressed with\Na thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330559,1332143}– What did you say?!\N– What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:15.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332269,1335647}Stone-baked hot potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337023,1338650}Piping hot sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:21.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338817,1341987}Wait! Mr. hot potato vendor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343697,1345198}What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345574,1348994}Why are you acting so strange?\NDid you want to buy a sweet potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:32.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349369,1352289}That's right! Anything wrong with that?!\NGo ahead and laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:33.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352330,1353707}How stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:35.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353790,1355750}That's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355876,1358044}I like them, too.\NSweet potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:40.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359337,1360380}Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:43.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361172,1363675}Let's go!\NWe can still catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:54.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372893,1374769}All right!\NThere it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:09.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387574,1389659}It's a patrol car!\NWhat are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:12.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389784,1392495}We can't stop!\NWhat am I supposed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:15.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1392871,1395707}You two on the bicycle up ahead!\NStop right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:19.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1396374,1399294}Oh, no!\NIt's my dad's patrol car!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:23.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399753,1403506}Blah Blah Blah Blah…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:26.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1404758,1406259}I'm sorry Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:28.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1406384,1408011}It's all because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:29.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408136,1409554}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:31.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409638,1411598}I'm used to Dad chewing me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:35.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412307,1415852}More importantly, I'm sorry we\Ndidn't get to buy the sweet potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1416645,1418605}Oh yeah! I forgot all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:40.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1418939,1420357}What do you mean you forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:45.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421983,1425278}Piping hot sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:48.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427572,1428740}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:50.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1428990,1430951}Sweet potato vendor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1439250,1441544}Meimi sure is taking a long time!
