Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.04,0:24:46.17,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1481042,1486172}before we shared our first kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.84,0:24:53.30,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1486840,1493304}for the reason I was crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.38,0:24:59.26,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1494389,1499269}I don't know what I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.72,0:25:07.81,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1499728,1507819}I feel like reminiscing a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:17.16,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1508194,1517162}Ah, tell me, what is true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.74,0:25:24.16,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1517746,1524169}Ah, I don't know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.37,0:25:31.21,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1524377,1531217}Hey, I want to scold
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.46,0:25:38.09,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1531468,1538099}the me inside the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.55,0:25:44.52,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1538558,1544522}I am struck with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.31,0:25:54.07,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1545315,1554074}Am I beautiful to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.62,0:26:05.46,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1558620,1565460}If I only had your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.12,0:26:11.25,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1566127,1571257}if you only stayed with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.96,0:26:18.76,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1571966,1578765}my happiness would reach no bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.47,0:26:24.64,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1579474,1584646}Nothing else would really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.89,0:26:32.86,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1584896,1592862}It's the first time in my life\NI feel like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.27,0:26:42.53,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1593279,1602539}Ah, you still don't know so many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.83,0:26:49.12,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1602831,1609129}Ah, even though you know me pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.50,0:26:56.21,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1609504,1616219}Hey, my biggest silent wish
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.46,0:27:02.97,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1616469,1622976}is for you to not end up hating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.68,0:27:09.69,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1623685,1629691}I'd be devastated if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.31,0:27:18.65,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1630316,1638658}Will my prayer be answered?
